<plot>The film is an observation on the eternity of a moment or a moment in eternity. The finding of an unaccompanied blood-stained suitcase drags the 'everyman' protagonist down the labyrinth of his own mind. Through corridors of this sinister world our hero faces his own demons and desires. Dreams, nightmares, greed and paranoia inhabit this land of half dark. And conscience knocks with a heavy hand.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?229393</url></doc>
